{"word":"H2026 - הָרַג - hârag - haw-rag' - Destroy","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">הָרַג</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>hârag"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>haw-rag'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Destroy"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கொல், கொலைசெய், அழி, வெட்டு, அடி, சங்காரம்பண்ணு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to kill, to slay, to murder, to destroy, mur derer, slayer, out of hand"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1)to kill, to slay"},{"paragraph":"2) to destroy, to ruin"},{"paragraph":"b) (Niphal) to be killed"},{"paragraph":"c) (Pual) to be killed, to be slain"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>smite</i> with deadly intent: - destroy, out of hand, kill, murder (-er), put to [death], make [slaughter], slay (-er), X surely."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2026 - הָרַג - hârag - haw-rag'/2026\">H2026</a>, <a href=\"#/H2027 - הֶרֶג - hereg - heh'-reg/2027\">H2027</a>, <a href=\"#/H2028 - הֲרֵגָה - hărêgâh - har-ay-gaw'/2028\">H2028</a>"}]}